{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4021_00_01","textHome":"我是塔鲁特……@因为聆听了主所派遣的天使大人的话语，@而获得了给法兰西带来光明的力量。@啊，不是……我并不是什么了不起的人！@我自己，只是一个来自乡村的少女而已。@叫我塔鲁特就可以了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":402100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4021_00_18","textHome":"我有时也会做着这样的梦，@我们的战争迎来结束，@上帝宽恕我们得以离开这个战场……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":402100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":402100,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":201,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4021_00_19","textHome":"怎么样？我也是能好好成长的吧！！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4021_00_20","textHome":"因为大家把力量借给了我，@所以我才能走到这里。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4021_00_21","textHome":"莉兹曾说我是能与她相匹的伙伴，@现在的我差不多有资格与她并肩作战了吧？@不行，光是这样还不能满足。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4021_00_22","textHome":"我想做的只是想拯救这个国家。@所以我不会把阻挡在我面前的人@都当作敌人来憎恨……@但是我不会原谅那些想要破坏一切的人。@我一定会挽救这一切的！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":402100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"chara":[{"id":402100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":402100,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":9.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":402100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4021_00_23","textHome":"「你在战场前线站立着的身姿……@你挥舞着的旗帜那就是『希望』本身」@那一天，莉兹对我说的话……@还有大家相信着的『希望』，我都深信不疑。@『希望』的旗帜就在这里……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":402100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":402100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":402100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":402100,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402150,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4021_50_24"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":402150}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402150,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402150,"motion":201}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402150,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_4021_50_25"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402150}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":402150,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":402150}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":402150,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_402